    q: 'Does Stickman Hook work on a Chromebook?',
    a: 'Yes. Stickman Hook runs as a standard HTML5 browser game, which means it works perfectly on Chromebooks — just open this page in Chrome and click Play. No extensions, plugins, or downloads are needed.',
  },
