    q: 'Why is Stickman Hook blocked at school?',
    a: 'Most schools block gaming sites as a category in their web filter, not specifically Stickman Hook. Because this site focuses on a single game with educational-adjacent content (physics, timing, coordination) it passes many standard filters — but network policies vary.',
