          <div class="fact-item"><span class="fact-label">Age rating</span><span class="fact-value">4+ (kid-friendly)</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-2" style="gap:2rem;align-items:start;">
        <div>
          <h2>Is Stickman Hook unblocked at school?</h2>
          <p>Yes — you can play Stickman Hook unblocked here, free and in full screen, with no download or login. Because it runs as an HTML5 browser game it loads on school and work networks, including Chromebooks, so you can swing through every level instantly.</p>
          <p>The game uses the same HTML5 technology that powers educational tools, which means many school firewalls don't flag it. You get the complete Stickman Hook experience — all 100+ levels, all skins, and both Classic and Grapple Hook modes — without any restrictions.</p>

          <h2>What is Stickman Hook?</h2>
          <p>Stickman Hook is a free physics-based swinging arcade game by Madbox. Your stickman fires a grappling hook at glowing anchor points and swings from one to the next, building momentum to reach the finish line. One button controls everything — hold to hook, release to fly. It's one of the most-played browser games on the internet, with over 100 million downloads across web and mobile.</p>

          <h2>How do I make Stickman Hook full screen?</h2>
          <p>Click the <strong>Fullscreen</strong> button below the game window, or press <strong>F11</strong> in your browser to go full screen. To exit, press F11 or Escape. On a Chromebook, use the full-screen key (usually at the top row) or the button in the game bar below the embed.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2>How to play Stickman Hook</h2>
          <p>There's just one input. Hold the mouse button or spacebar to hook the nearest anchor, then release to launch. Here's the quick version:</p>
          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><p>Click/hold (or tap on mobile) to fire your grappling hook at an anchor point.</p></div>
            <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><p>Swing on the rope — timing matters. Build momentum in the arc.</p></div>
            <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><p>Release at the peak of your swing to launch toward the next anchor.</p></div>
          </div>

          <div class="tip-box">
            <p><strong>School tip:</strong> Use headphones if sound is on — the game has upbeat music. You can mute it in the game settings (gear icon) without affecting gameplay.</p>
          </div>

          <h2>Other versions — Unblocked 76, 66, 67, 77, 99</h2>
