          <h2>Can I play on a school computer or Chromebook?</h2>
          <p>Chromebooks run Chrome OS and play HTML5 games natively in the browser — no plugins required. This site is fully compatible. Just open the page in Chrome (or any browser on a school computer), click the game, and start swinging. If your school's filter blocks this URL, ask your IT admin or try the search terms "stickman hook unblocked github" for alternative hosts.</p>
